@model GrcMvc.Models.DTOs.CreateAssessmentDto
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Assessment_Create_Title"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mb-3">
        <div class="col">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-plus-circle"></i> @L["Assessment_Create_New"]</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col text-end">
            <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> @L["BackToList"]
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <form asp-action="Create">
                <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="text-danger"></div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Name" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Name"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="Name" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Assessment_Name_Placeholder"]" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Name" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="AssessmentNumber" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Number"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="AssessmentNumber" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Assessment_Number_Placeholder"]" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="AssessmentNumber" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="AssessmentCode" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Code"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="AssessmentCode" class="form-control" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="AssessmentCode" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Type" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Type"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="Type" class="form-select">
                                <option value="">@L["Form_SelectType"]</option>
                                <option value="Risk">@L["Assessment_Type_Risk"]</option>
                                <option value="Control">@L["Assessment_Type_Control"]</option>
                                <option value="Compliance">@L["Assessment_Type_Compliance"]</option>
                                <option value="Security">@L["Assessment_Type_Security"]</option>
                            </select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Type" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="StartDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_StartDate"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="StartDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="StartDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ScheduledDate" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_ScheduledDate"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="ScheduledDate" class="form-control" type="date" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="ScheduledDate" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Description" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_Description"]</label>
                    <textarea asp-for="Description" class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Description" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="AssignedTo" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_AssignedTo"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="AssignedTo" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Assessment_AssignedTo_Placeholder"]" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="AssignedTo" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="RiskId" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_RelatedRisk"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="RiskId" class="form-select" asp-items="ViewBag.RiskId">
                                <option value="">@L["Form_None"]</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="form-group mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="ControlId" class="control-label fw-bold">@L["Assessment_RelatedControl"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="ControlId" class="form-select" asp-items="ViewBag.ControlId">
                                <option value="">@L["Form_None"]</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group mt-4">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> @L["CreateAssessment"]
                    </button>
                    <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">@L["Cancel"]</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @{await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");}
}
